title.narrative: MQSUN+ - (Path) Nutrition Technical Assistance for DFID country offices and Sun Movement Secretariat

description.narrative: This activity (MQSUN+ - (Path) Nutrition Technical Assistance for DFID country offices and Sun Movement Secretariat) is a component of Technical Assistance for Nutrition reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £11,565,210. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Basic nutrition. , with the following implementing partners: Path. The start date is 01-05-2016 and the end date is 30-11-2021.
